name: AFL Evolution Plus Season Pack 2018
summary:
AFL Evolution Plus Season Pack 2018 Includes both the AFL Evolution Base Game, as well as updates to playing rosters and the all new Optus Stadium.

Season Pack 2018 Includes

- New Team Rosters
- New 2018 Season
- New Optus Stadium
- Additional leagues ( NEAFL, SANFL & WAFL)
